data.description: Welcome to 200 Lucas Way! Perfectly situated near Hwy 316 between Athens and Winder, this 3 bed 2 bath stepless ranch sits on a large corner lot in the NO HOA neighborhood of Cofer Estates. Move-in ready with LVP flooring throughout and updated light fixtures, this home is ready for your personal touches! Split bedroom plan with master bedroom featuring his/her walk-in closets and spacious ensuite. Two secondary bedrooms and another full bath are located on the opposite side of the home. Airy kitchen w/ breakfast area overlooking the family room and separate dining room. Fenced-in backyard with storage shed. Let's make this house your home!
